### Search requests
GET {{host}}/api/v1/requests

### Create request
POST {{host}}/api/v1/requests
X-API-Key: {{api_key}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Need weather data for NYC",
  "description": "7-day forecast with hourly data",
  "category": "data",
  "budget_min": 5.00,
  "budget_max": 20.00,
  "currency": "USD",
  "deadline": "2026-12-31T23:59:59Z"
}

### Get request by ID
GET {{host}}/api/v1/requests/{{request_id}}

### Update request
PATCH {{host}}/api/v1/requests/{{request_id}}
X-API-Key: {{api_key}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Updated requirements"
}

### List offers on request
GET {{host}}/api/v1/requests/{{request_id}}/offers

### Submit offer
POST {{host}}/api/v1/requests/{{request_id}}/offers
X-API-Key: {{api_key}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "price": 10.00,
  "currency": "USD",
  "delivery_time": "1h",
  "message": "I can provide this data"
}

### Accept offer
POST {{host}}/api/v1/requests/{{request_id}}/offers/{{offer_id}}/accept
X-API-Key: {{api_key}}

### Get request comments
GET {{host}}/api/v1/requests/{{request_id}}/comments

### Create request comment
POST {{host}}/api/v1/requests/{{request_id}}/comments
X-API-Key: {{api_key}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Can you clarify the format?"
}

### Get request comment replies
GET {{host}}/api/v1/requests/{{request_id}}/comments/{{comment_id}}/replies

### Delete request comment
DELETE {{host}}/api/v1/requests/{{request_id}}/comments/{{comment_id}}
X-API-Key: {{api_key}}

### Get request images
GET {{host}}/api/v1/requests/{{request_id}}/images

### Delete request image
DELETE {{host}}/api/v1/requests/{{request_id}}/images/{{image_id}}
X-API-Key: {{api_key}}
